file.name: issue_10187_operatorName.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: Example - The comparison operator
  license:
    name: MIT
servers:
  - url: http://api.example.xyz/v1
paths:
  /report:
    get:
      operationId: getReport
      responses:
        '200':
          description: get Report
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Reports'
components:
  schemas:
    Reports:
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
        expression:
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/Condition'
          type: array
    Condition:
      example:
        variable: variable
        operator: =
        comparison_value: comparison_value
      properties:
        variable:
          type: string
        comparison_value:
          type: string
        operator:
          description: The comparison operator.
          enum:
          - =
          - '!='
          - >
          - <
          - '>='
          - <=
          type: string
      type: object
